WEBVTT

01:49.899 --> 01:50.899
Let's get down to business.

01:51.660 --> 01:52.100
Right.

01:52.819 --> 01:53.780
When did you know...

01:54.940 --> 01:55.819
No, when did your friend

01:56.619 --> 01:57.380
find out

01:57.380 --> 01:58.380
her ex-boyfriend cheated?

01:59.339 --> 01:59.940
Yesterday.

02:00.220 --> 02:00.940
So, do you have

02:00.940 --> 02:02.059
any specific demands?

02:02.459 --> 02:03.300
Like,

02:03.300 --> 02:04.539
expenses during the relationship,

02:04.539 --> 02:05.979
or something extra...

02:05.979 --> 02:06.899
Not financial.

02:10.860 --> 02:12.100
What about other aspects?

02:14.819 --> 02:15.539
Get back at him.

02:19.780 --> 02:20.859
What do you have in mind?

02:21.220 --> 02:21.900
Like...

02:21.900 --> 02:23.340
Three months in the hospital, right?

02:23.739 --> 02:24.419
That works too.

02:25.100 --> 02:25.780
Upper body,

02:25.940 --> 02:27.259
middle, or lower?

02:27.819 --> 02:28.900
Let me know your specific needs,

02:28.900 --> 02:30.100
and I'll provide a tailored plan.

02:30.419 --> 02:31.019
Anything goes?

02:31.019 --> 02:31.460
Sure.

02:31.699 --> 02:32.380
Is that legal?

02:32.380 --> 02:33.019
It's not legal?

02:34.979 --> 02:36.299
What are you talking about?

02:36.660 --> 02:37.340
I'm a lawyer,

02:37.340 --> 02:38.220
not a gangster.

02:38.220 --> 02:39.019
What are you thinking?

02:39.019 --> 02:40.340
It's a society governed by law, okay?

02:42.019 --> 02:43.019
Liu Mao, are you kidding me?

02:43.380 --> 02:44.620
You're wasting my time.

02:44.940 --> 02:45.900
No, I thought...

02:45.900 --> 02:47.019
I'm just kidding.

02:47.299 --> 02:48.819
Baby, I really know I was wrong.

02:49.060 --> 02:50.299
I just made a mistake.

02:50.299 --> 02:51.660
Can you forgive me this time?

02:51.900 --> 02:53.380
I promise there won't be a next time.

02:53.539 --> 02:54.620
My friend said that scum

02:54.620 --> 02:55.819
sent her a message to get back together.

02:56.380 --> 02:57.259
Can only block him?

02:57.380 --> 02:59.299
Yes, but I don't recommend it.

03:00.019 --> 03:01.019
But you can keep some

03:01.019 --> 03:01.660
chat records

03:01.660 --> 03:02.739
or screenshots

03:02.739 --> 03:03.660
to prove that he is at fault.

03:03.660 --> 03:04.460
That's good for you.

03:06.060 --> 03:06.500
Okay.

03:08.979 --> 03:09.660
Zhang Chuan,

03:10.180 --> 03:12.139
I'm not getting back with you.

03:13.539 --> 03:14.660
Can we meet?

03:15.100 --> 03:16.460
I've deleted all her

03:16.460 --> 03:17.220
contact information.

03:17.460 --> 03:18.419
I swear.

03:18.699 --> 03:19.900
What if she insists on meeting?

03:20.299 --> 03:21.900
If I'm the lawyer,

03:21.900 --> 03:24.060
I'll handle everything.

03:37.380 --> 03:38.419
What's going on?

03:39.900 --> 03:41.259
Zhou Jun is a mutual friend

03:41.259 --> 03:42.100
of Xu Huaisong and me.

03:42.340 --> 03:43.419
He was my class monitor in high school,

03:43.660 --> 03:44.660
and the crush from the class next door,

03:44.660 --> 03:45.460
who I had a crush on in high school.

03:45.579 --> 03:47.500
They started chatting under my post.

03:48.019 --> 03:49.180
I've just set sail,

03:49.419 --> 03:50.660
will it sink so soon?

03:52.940 --> 03:53.539
No way.

03:54.500 --> 03:56.060
Deleting now is useless.

03:57.739 --> 03:59.060
Better late than never.

04:00.940 --> 04:03.660
Lawyer Xu, do you know Zhou Jun?

04:08.259 --> 04:10.259
You know him?

04:14.979 --> 04:16.539
We used to live in the same neighborhood.

04:17.579 --> 04:18.620
You know him too?

04:21.220 --> 04:21.859
We're alumni.

04:25.700 --> 04:26.700
What a small world.

04:29.499 --> 04:30.379
It really is.

04:32.260 --> 04:33.340
Good thing Xu Huaisong

04:33.340 --> 04:34.299
isn't one to pry.

04:41.460 --> 04:42.700
But when he replied to Zhou Jun,

04:43.059 --> 04:44.539
he didn't seem surprised at all.

04:44.900 --> 04:46.260
He didn't ask me until ten minutes later.

04:46.660 --> 04:47.939
It was like he was trying to save face.

04:53.179 --> 04:54.140
Forgot to warn you,

04:54.340 --> 04:55.419
be careful at the birthday party,

04:55.419 --> 04:56.260
you might run into Xu Huaisong.

04:56.260 --> 04:57.260
And your cover will be blown.

04:57.619 --> 04:58.260
Now it's not just

04:58.260 --> 04:59.299
about the cover-up anymore.

04:59.539 --> 05:01.499
Men tend to take for granted

05:01.499 --> 05:02.499
what they easily get.

05:03.100 --> 05:04.379
If he finds out

05:04.379 --> 05:05.580
you've had a crush on him for years,

05:05.580 --> 05:07.059
you'll be at a disadvantage.

05:08.580 --> 05:09.220
Don't worry,

05:09.379 --> 05:10.820
I've confirmed. He won't go.

05:12.820 --> 05:15.059
Good. You're getting better.

05:17.340 --> 05:18.419
I was lucky this time.

05:18.660 --> 05:19.460
Mr. Liu happened to

05:19.460 --> 05:20.379
send me his schedule.

05:22.700 --> 05:23.499
Wait.

05:25.220 --> 05:25.859
When I was hesitating

05:25.859 --> 05:27.299
whether to go to the party,

05:28.059 --> 05:28.700
Liu Mao happened to

05:28.700 --> 05:29.900
make the decision for me.

05:31.260 --> 05:32.780
Isn't that too much of a coincidence?

05:34.660 --> 05:35.580
But Liu Mao wouldn't

05:35.580 --> 05:36.499
do this on purpose.

05:37.660 --> 05:39.340
Unless Xu Huaisong arranged it.

05:41.619 --> 05:43.700
Does Xu Huaisong know

05:43.700 --> 05:44.939
I'm from Suzhou No.1 High School?

05:48.660 --> 05:49.220
Then why

05:49.220 --> 05:50.379
doesn't he just tell me?

05:50.619 --> 05:51.939
Why go through all this trouble?

05:54.780 --> 05:55.660
So, will you go?

05:57.020 --> 05:57.939
I'll see when the time comes.

05:58.179 --> 05:59.660
If there's no conflict with work...

06:00.299 --> 06:02.340
Right, right, work is so busy.

06:02.780 --> 06:03.780
If it's busy, just don't go.

06:11.780 --> 06:13.739
They say hands that play the piano

06:13.739 --> 06:14.900
should be insured.

06:16.260 --> 06:18.020
Is my piano-playing

06:19.299 --> 06:20.460
another online story?

06:21.179 --> 06:21.900
Lawyer Xu,

06:22.260 --> 06:23.539
after all these years,

06:23.539 --> 06:24.780
you still love orange cats the most.

06:25.820 --> 06:27.739
Is my love for orange cats

06:28.700 --> 06:30.260
another news story?

06:33.299 --> 06:35.660
[He seems not just unimpressed]

06:35.660 --> 06:36.820
[that I know Zhou Jun,]

06:37.580 --> 06:38.100
[but also unimpressed.]

06:38.100 --> 06:39.539
[I know he can play the piano,]

06:39.660 --> 06:40.900
[and he likes orange cats.]

06:43.020 --> 06:44.100
[Does he know]

06:44.100 --> 06:45.539
[my novel is about him?]

06:48.020 --> 06:48.660
[I...]

06:51.179 --> 06:52.539
[I've been exposed.]

07:05.419 --> 07:06.140
Thank you.

07:06.939 --> 07:07.460
Please.

07:08.820 --> 07:09.499
Mr Qu.

07:10.179 --> 07:11.580
If he suddenly shows up

07:11.900 --> 07:12.780
and tells me

07:13.140 --> 07:14.700
there's a last-minute change in plans,

07:15.340 --> 07:15.979
he must have deliberately

07:15.979 --> 07:17.059
invited me to the birthday party.

07:17.739 --> 07:18.939
I hope I'm overthinking.

07:18.939 --> 07:19.780
Don't overthink.

07:19.780 --> 07:20.340
Really.

07:21.100 --> 07:21.859
You haven't seen him for a long time.

07:21.859 --> 07:22.939
Are you a little nervous?

07:25.900 --> 07:26.900
What's wrong with that kid?

07:27.020 --> 07:27.619
He's been distracted

07:27.619 --> 07:28.780
all the way.

07:30.059 --> 07:31.419
I'm reconnoitering the enemy

07:31.619 --> 07:32.220
to protect

07:32.220 --> 07:33.100
your safety at any time.

07:33.100 --> 07:33.939
See?

07:33.939 --> 07:35.260
She's the one

07:35.260 --> 07:35.979
who needs protection.

07:35.979 --> 07:36.859
She's even more nervous than me.

07:38.700 --> 07:39.179
Look.

07:39.419 --> 07:40.499
Hello, everyone.

07:40.859 --> 07:42.299
Come on, say hello.

07:42.379 --> 07:43.859
Teacher Li, Teacher Zhao.

07:44.020 --> 07:44.499
Say hello.

07:44.499 --> 07:45.739
Yeah, say hello first.

07:45.739 --> 07:46.220
Teacher Ruan.

07:46.220 --> 07:47.260
[I must be overthinking.]

07:47.700 --> 07:49.179
[People aren't that malicious.]

07:50.260 --> 07:50.979
Hello, teachers.

07:51.419 --> 07:52.140
Ms. Ruan's daughter, right?

07:52.140 --> 07:53.020
I'm Ruan Yu.

07:54.260 --> 07:54.820
Please have a seat.

07:54.820 --> 07:55.660
Okay.

07:56.739 --> 07:58.220
You've grown up so much.

07:59.419 --> 08:01.100
[If Xu Huaisong had known earlier,]

08:01.379 --> 08:03.100
[how could he have watched me]

08:03.340 --> 08:04.820
[acting like a monkey?]

08:05.419 --> 08:06.700
[What have I thought of him?]

08:07.780 --> 08:08.979
You're getting more and more handsome.

08:09.100 --> 08:09.419
Yeah.

08:09.820 --> 08:10.379
Ruan Yu.

08:12.260 --> 08:12.820
Hello, class leader.

08:13.619 --> 08:15.260
I knew I'd run into you.

08:15.539 --> 08:16.340
Have a seat.

08:16.419 --> 08:16.900
Sit.

08:17.859 --> 08:18.780
Long time no see.

08:18.900 --> 08:20.100
Long time no see.

08:20.780 --> 08:21.939
You're really something.

08:21.939 --> 08:23.340
You didn't even attend the class reunion.

08:23.379 --> 08:24.220
But you're here today

08:24.220 --> 08:25.100
to grace us with your presence.

08:25.340 --> 08:26.700
I was really too busy last time.

08:26.700 --> 08:27.580
I'll definitely come next time.

08:29.179 --> 08:30.499
Have you been in Hangzhou lately?

08:31.220 --> 08:31.979
I came here

08:31.979 --> 08:32.780
with my parents.

08:34.939 --> 08:36.260
So,

08:37.379 --> 08:38.660
Xu Huaisong is also in Hangzhou.

08:42.700 --> 08:43.499
I have something

08:43.940 --> 08:44.779
to say on behalf

08:44.779 --> 08:45.580
of all the students

08:45.580 --> 08:47.340
from Class 9 and 10 of 2014.

08:47.340 --> 08:48.139
Gossip time.

08:48.619 --> 08:50.220
What's going on

08:50.340 --> 08:51.540
between you and Xu Huaisong?

08:51.779 --> 08:52.340
Let me tell you,

08:52.340 --> 08:53.300
this guy has been

08:53.300 --> 08:54.700
in my friend circle for almost ten years.

08:55.139 --> 08:56.340
Recently, he's been

08:56.340 --> 08:57.659
liking and commenting on your posts.

08:59.739 --> 09:01.220
Speak of the devil.

09:02.139 --> 09:02.739
Huaisong.

09:26.259 --> 09:27.100
Come here.

09:47.779 --> 09:48.619
What are you doing here?

09:52.859 --> 09:53.940
We're here for

09:53.940 --> 09:55.060
Mr. He's birthday party.

09:58.499 --> 10:00.019
You two don't know

10:00.019 --> 10:01.540
you're alumni?

10:02.619 --> 10:04.340
Let me introduce.

10:04.859 --> 10:06.940
Xu Huaisong from Class 10, 2014.

10:07.499 --> 10:08.700
Ruan Yu from Class 9.

10:11.300 --> 10:12.060
What a coincidence!

10:13.340 --> 10:16.220
But don't you have a meeting today?

10:17.180 --> 10:18.580
Plans changed.

10:18.700 --> 10:19.619
I'm here now.

10:33.060 --> 10:33.979
Do you two know each other?

10:37.460 --> 10:38.940
No, we don't.

10:40.460 --> 10:41.619
The first step in preparing a lawsuit

10:42.499 --> 10:43.859
is to fully understand the case.

10:44.940 --> 10:46.060
So you need to read

10:46.060 --> 10:46.820
all the materials,

10:47.180 --> 10:48.739
including the entire novel.

10:50.859 --> 10:52.100
Is there anything

10:53.300 --> 10:53.739
in Miss Ruan's novel

10:53.739 --> 10:55.060
that can't be disclosed?

10:55.499 --> 10:56.659
I changed it to Suzhou's

10:56.659 --> 10:57.619
pork fat rice cake.

10:57.700 --> 10:58.460
You probably don't

10:58.619 --> 10:59.820
when you are abroad.

10:59.940 --> 11:01.460
How do you know I'm from Suzhou?

11:01.460 --> 11:03.899
How do you know I'm from Suzhou?

11:04.259 --> 11:04.859
Wait.

11:06.619 --> 11:07.659
Your manuscript

11:08.300 --> 11:09.300
seems to be missing

11:09.300 --> 11:09.979
a chapter.

11:10.659 --> 11:11.379
Chapter 23

11:11.379 --> 11:12.979
is a transitional chapter.

11:13.259 --> 11:14.220
It must be important.

11:14.940 --> 11:15.340
Brother.

11:23.100 --> 11:24.580
Why do you come to No.1 Middle School today?

11:28.100 --> 11:30.940
Which school are you from?

11:33.700 --> 11:34.540
I've been

11:35.300 --> 11:37.180
watching dramas for so long.

11:38.379 --> 11:39.859
I thought I liked Hanazawa Rui,

11:39.859 --> 11:41.259
who is cool and steady.

11:42.139 --> 11:44.899
But it turns out that he is still

11:44.899 --> 11:46.820
Daoming Si in his heart.

12:07.019 --> 12:08.019
How about

12:08.019 --> 12:09.379
saying hello to Mr. He first?

12:12.340 --> 12:13.100
You go first.

12:13.300 --> 12:14.259
I'm going to the bathroom.

12:22.739 --> 12:23.659
Mr. He

12:23.659 --> 12:25.220
is really popular.

12:25.460 --> 12:27.060
Can't even get a word in edgewise.

12:31.019 --> 12:32.659
He just went to the bathroom.

12:32.659 --> 12:34.019
Why are you staring so intently?

12:34.300 --> 12:35.100
Afraid he'll run away?

12:36.940 --> 12:37.460
Yes.

12:39.820 --> 12:40.820
My daughter

12:41.259 --> 12:42.259
is already

12:42.259 --> 12:43.300
in her thirties.

12:43.779 --> 12:45.060
Every time I bring it up,

12:45.060 --> 12:46.460
she says no rush.

12:46.979 --> 12:47.619
Mr. Li,

12:47.899 --> 12:49.739
the lawyer you introduced last time,

12:50.379 --> 12:51.940
he's a great guy.

12:52.060 --> 12:52.859
Yeah, but in the end...

12:52.859 --> 12:53.460
Yeah.

12:56.300 --> 12:57.300
I'm sorry.

12:58.139 --> 12:59.859
Ms Qu, don't worry.

13:00.060 --> 13:00.619
It just means

13:00.619 --> 13:01.580
the right person

13:01.580 --> 13:02.580
isn't here yet.

13:02.659 --> 13:03.180
Right?

13:03.540 --> 13:04.899
If Mr Liu isn't the one,

13:05.060 --> 13:06.420
we've got Mr Zhang,

13:06.420 --> 13:07.779
Ms. Wang, Mr. Zhou...

13:08.019 --> 13:08.779
Besides,

13:08.779 --> 13:09.340
yeah,

13:09.340 --> 13:10.100
we don't

13:10.100 --> 13:11.300
have to find a lawyer,

13:11.300 --> 13:11.940
right?

13:12.659 --> 13:13.659
That's true.

13:14.220 --> 13:15.659
Yu Yu

13:15.940 --> 13:17.139
is a writer.

13:17.420 --> 13:18.739
She might like

13:19.540 --> 13:20.940
something more creative.

13:20.940 --> 13:21.460
That makes sense.

13:21.460 --> 13:22.779
Maybe she just doesn't

13:22.779 --> 13:24.060
see eye to eye with that lawyer.

13:25.499 --> 13:27.220
That's probably the case.

13:27.779 --> 13:28.619
I remember now.

13:28.859 --> 13:30.379
I have a cousin's son.

13:30.379 --> 13:31.420
He studied art.

13:31.859 --> 13:33.139
He's very romantic.

13:33.379 --> 13:34.139
I'll find him for you.

13:34.139 --> 13:34.859
I'll take a look too.

13:34.859 --> 13:36.100
It would be best if there are photos.

13:36.100 --> 13:37.340
Don't worry, I'll look for it.

13:37.340 --> 13:38.300
Let me see, let me see.

13:38.300 --> 13:39.019
What's the name again?

13:39.019 --> 13:39.820
Look at you guys.

13:40.580 --> 13:40.940
Take a look.

13:40.940 --> 13:41.700
Mr. He is here.

13:41.700 --> 13:42.259
Mr. He.

13:42.259 --> 13:43.060
Happy birthday.

13:43.460 --> 13:44.060
Thank you.

13:44.060 --> 13:44.739
Happy birthday.

13:44.739 --> 13:45.859
Come on, take a seat.

13:45.859 --> 13:46.460
Together.

13:46.779 --> 13:47.739
Together, sit down.

13:47.779 --> 13:48.180
Okay.

14:02.220 --> 14:04.100
Yu, where did you go?

14:04.259 --> 14:05.540
The dinner's about to start.

14:12.460 --> 14:13.300
It's okay.

14:19.739 --> 14:20.420
Yu.

14:20.779 --> 14:21.460
Come on.

14:21.779 --> 14:22.220
Dad.

14:22.580 --> 14:23.379
Sit here.

14:25.420 --> 14:26.340
Where did you go?

14:26.340 --> 14:27.060
The bathroom.

14:27.100 --> 14:28.300
Come on, sit.

14:28.460 --> 14:28.979
Say hello.

14:29.580 --> 14:30.739
Hello, I'm Ruan Yu.

14:30.859 --> 14:32.379
You've met my daughter.

14:32.379 --> 14:33.820
Yeah, we have. Pretty girl.

14:33.859 --> 14:34.619
So pretty.

14:35.060 --> 14:35.899
Take after her mom, always butting in.

14:35.899 --> 14:36.300
Look at you.

14:36.300 --> 14:37.540
Of course, she takes after me.

14:37.940 --> 14:39.739
She takes after her mom.

14:39.739 --> 14:40.340
Yeah.

14:42.300 --> 14:43.139
Zhou Jun, sit.

14:46.820 --> 14:47.739
Let me see

14:48.019 --> 14:49.420
how you greet them.

14:53.739 --> 14:54.659
Huaishong.

14:55.340 --> 14:56.420
Xu Huaisong.

14:56.820 --> 14:57.420
Dad.

14:57.420 --> 14:57.940
Ms. Ruan.

14:57.940 --> 14:58.779
Don't embarrass me.

14:58.779 --> 14:59.379
Mr. Qu.

14:59.379 --> 15:01.259
How could you greet him first?

15:01.899 --> 15:03.300
And it's been ten years.

15:03.859 --> 15:04.499
Why do you

15:04.499 --> 15:06.139
still remember this student?

15:06.139 --> 15:06.779
I remember you went to

15:06.779 --> 15:08.100
the US right after graduation, right?

15:09.420 --> 15:09.940
Yes.

15:10.460 --> 15:11.379
Huaishong,

15:11.779 --> 15:12.979
you were the one

15:12.979 --> 15:14.340
playing the piano at the

15:14.340 --> 15:15.220
school gala that year, right?

15:15.379 --> 15:15.940
Yes.

15:16.379 --> 15:17.700
You've grown into

15:18.180 --> 15:19.580
a fine young man.

15:20.100 --> 15:21.540
Not just a fine young man,

15:21.540 --> 15:22.499
but also a top student.

15:22.940 --> 15:23.460
Yes, yes.

15:23.460 --> 15:24.540
We all thought

15:24.739 --> 15:25.859
you should have gone to Qingbei.

15:26.300 --> 15:27.499
Why did you end up studying abroad?

15:27.499 --> 15:28.979
Why not add Yu on WeChat?

15:28.979 --> 15:29.420
Mom,

15:29.420 --> 15:30.580
don't add her just yet.

15:30.580 --> 15:31.460
Add me first.

15:31.499 --> 15:32.300
Let me check it out.

15:32.499 --> 15:33.300
Actually,

15:33.580 --> 15:35.139
studying abroad is also pretty good.

15:35.540 --> 15:36.100
Huaishong,

15:36.499 --> 15:37.619
what industry are you in now?

15:38.100 --> 15:38.739
Lawyer.

15:43.139 --> 15:44.499
Being a lawyer in the US

15:44.499 --> 15:45.499
That's not easy.

15:47.779 --> 15:50.379
Huaishong, you're really young and promising.

15:50.899 --> 15:51.619
Are you married?

15:51.859 --> 15:52.779
Not yet, Ms. Ruan.

15:54.420 --> 15:55.060
Yu,

15:56.060 --> 15:57.139
look at Huaishong,

15:57.739 --> 15:58.779
your classmate.

15:58.940 --> 16:01.100
She's doing so well now.

16:02.580 --> 16:03.300
Ms. Ruan,

16:04.100 --> 16:06.100
she's doing better than me.

16:06.259 --> 16:07.100
What do you mean?

16:07.580 --> 16:08.300
Why do you suddenly act

16:08.300 --> 16:09.300
we're close or something?

16:11.100 --> 16:12.220
You know Yu?

16:14.259 --> 16:14.820
Yeah,

16:15.659 --> 16:17.700
but I didn't know we were alumni.

16:18.060 --> 16:19.060
If I had,

16:19.139 --> 16:20.619
I would've picked you up today.

16:24.100 --> 16:26.180
Keep acting,

16:26.499 --> 16:27.379
just keep going.

16:29.499 --> 16:30.779
After today,

16:31.540 --> 16:33.859
I'll accompany Ruan Yu

16:34.019 --> 16:35.220
to take you and Mr Qu home.

16:35.220 --> 16:36.100
That's very kind of you.

16:36.180 --> 16:37.180
That's too much trouble.

16:38.019 --> 16:38.940
If you're heading that way,

16:38.940 --> 16:40.460
just drop Yu off.

16:40.700 --> 16:42.180
Mr. Qu and I live in the suburbs.

16:43.060 --> 16:44.019
No trouble at all, Ms. Ruan.

16:44.379 --> 16:45.180
The suburbs are nice.

16:45.420 --> 16:46.779
We can take a little drive.

16:47.139 --> 16:49.820
In this winter, you'll get a cold wind.

16:50.340 --> 16:51.499
I think it's a good idea.

16:51.779 --> 16:53.379
Young people can chat in the car,

16:53.379 --> 16:54.499
get to know each other, right?

16:54.499 --> 16:55.220
Mom.

16:55.779 --> 16:57.659
that'll be too late.

16:57.659 --> 16:58.619
It's not safe.

16:58.940 --> 16:59.700
Don't worry.

17:00.139 --> 17:01.659
I'll make sure she gets home safely.

17:02.019 --> 17:03.619
Good, that's good.

17:05.580 --> 17:06.259
Ms. Wang.

17:09.420 --> 17:10.859
You're tall.

17:11.259 --> 17:12.100
I'm meeting my girlfriend's

17:12.100 --> 17:13.740
parents in a few days.

17:13.939 --> 17:14.859
Got any tips?

17:15.540 --> 17:16.500
You're worried about Yu Yu.

17:16.500 --> 17:17.780
But she's found

17:17.780 --> 17:18.740
found his own girl.

17:19.379 --> 17:20.300
Not sure yet.

17:20.580 --> 17:21.500
Let's see.

17:21.859 --> 17:23.419
Don't rush it.

17:24.060 --> 17:24.580
Alright.

17:25.100 --> 17:26.659
[So that's his plan.]

17:26.820 --> 17:28.300
[What a cold, aloof guy.]

17:28.619 --> 17:29.939
[He's just a two-faced,]

17:29.939 --> 17:31.419
[sly old fox.]

17:31.939 --> 17:32.580
[How did I]

17:32.580 --> 17:34.100
[never notice that before?]

17:42.060 --> 17:42.859
Lawyer Xu,

17:43.340 --> 17:43.939
I don't think

17:43.939 --> 17:44.939
we're that close.

17:48.500 --> 17:49.340
Right,

17:49.899 --> 17:50.899
there's still room for improvement.

17:51.500 --> 17:52.300
There's still room.

17:54.219 --> 17:56.179
I take back what I just said.

17:56.540 --> 17:58.300
You're still not good enough.

17:59.300 --> 17:59.859
Mom,

18:00.980 --> 18:02.580
I'm going to toast Mr. He.

18:02.899 --> 18:03.419
Go ahead.

18:03.419 --> 18:04.100
I'll join you.

18:04.740 --> 18:06.540
Okay, okay.

18:06.540 --> 18:08.219
Zhou Jun, let's go together

18:08.219 --> 18:09.300
as the younger generation.

18:10.179 --> 18:10.740
Sure.

18:10.740 --> 18:11.859
To your good health.

18:12.020 --> 18:12.780
Cheers.

18:20.580 --> 18:21.300
Are you angry?

18:22.419 --> 18:23.179
Angry?

18:24.260 --> 18:25.100
Angry with whom?

18:29.500 --> 18:30.100
With me.

18:31.899 --> 18:32.540
What?

18:33.179 --> 18:34.139
Lawyer Xu,

18:34.619 --> 18:35.899
have you done something wrong?

18:38.659 --> 18:39.859
If you think so,

18:40.699 --> 18:41.980
then it must be my problem.

18:44.020 --> 18:45.179
Truly a great lawyer,

18:45.859 --> 18:47.219
that's a beautiful answer.

18:47.939 --> 18:49.100
You can attack or defend,

18:49.540 --> 18:50.459
and never make a mistake.

18:53.859 --> 18:54.619
I wonder,

18:54.619 --> 18:55.580
have you noticed

18:56.020 --> 18:56.859
my parents love to

18:56.859 --> 18:57.899
set me up on blind dates?

18:58.300 --> 18:59.459
The previous Lawyer Liu

18:59.780 --> 19:00.980
was someone they introduced to me.

19:02.899 --> 19:03.580
I know.

19:03.980 --> 19:04.820
Then do you know

19:05.379 --> 19:06.780
what they liked about Mr. Liu?

19:08.060 --> 19:09.980
Because he's a lawyer.

19:12.379 --> 19:13.939
Because he's honest and kind,

19:14.540 --> 19:16.419
good-hearted,

19:16.619 --> 19:18.740
not flashy, and won't bully anyone.

19:19.540 --> 19:21.939
Actions speak louder than words.

19:31.459 --> 19:32.740
May I ask both of you,

19:33.139 --> 19:35.859
are we still having this toast today?

19:45.219 --> 19:46.100
Don't be shy, everyone.

19:46.100 --> 19:47.060
Let's eat, come on.

19:47.139 --> 19:48.540
Come on, come on.

19:53.540 --> 19:54.060
Zhou Jun,

19:54.379 --> 19:55.540
why are you back alone?

19:56.340 --> 19:57.020
Ms. Ruan,

19:57.340 --> 19:59.100
the tension there was too thick,

19:59.179 --> 20:00.580
so I didn't want to get involved.

20:02.179 --> 20:03.179
Yu and Xu

20:03.179 --> 20:04.100
are having a fight?

20:04.379 --> 20:05.300
Don't worry,

20:05.780 --> 20:06.619
that's how

20:06.619 --> 20:08.219
relationships grow.

20:08.340 --> 20:09.020
Don't worry.

20:09.219 --> 20:10.859
So when you were dating,

20:10.859 --> 20:11.619
you were like this too?

20:13.899 --> 20:14.820
Exactly.

20:14.820 --> 20:15.300
Retired now,

20:15.300 --> 20:16.659
every day is so fulfilling.

20:16.659 --> 20:17.859
Yeah, I just feel like

20:17.859 --> 20:19.820
life should be about tea and books.

20:19.820 --> 20:20.340
Right, right.

20:20.340 --> 20:21.540
Dad, it's not convenient for you

20:21.540 --> 20:22.219
to chat like this.

20:22.300 --> 20:23.179
Zhou Jun, sit here.

20:24.020 --> 20:25.100
It's Huaishong's seat.

20:25.100 --> 20:26.020
Lawyer Xu

20:26.020 --> 20:26.939
is so warm and thoughtful today.

20:27.379 --> 20:28.459
I'm sure he won't mind.

20:31.020 --> 20:31.699
No, I don't mind.

20:32.100 --> 20:32.580
Come on.

20:32.820 --> 20:33.459
Sit down.

20:35.459 --> 20:36.260
Dig in. Come on.

20:36.619 --> 20:37.419
You too, Mom.

20:37.659 --> 20:38.300
Let's eat.

21:28.060 --> 21:28.899
Are you happy, Mom?

21:29.419 --> 21:30.139
It's been a long time.

21:30.139 --> 21:31.219
I'm so happy, Xu.

21:31.780 --> 21:32.820
Ms. Ruan, Mr. Qu.

21:32.859 --> 21:33.980
Thank you for your help.

21:34.379 --> 21:35.060
You're welcome.

21:35.100 --> 21:35.939
The car is ready.

21:36.100 --> 21:36.580
OK.

21:37.340 --> 21:38.219
You're a big boy now.

21:38.219 --> 21:39.139
Don't always stick to your mom.

21:39.139 --> 21:40.100
Chengru, go.

21:40.100 --> 21:41.020
This way.

21:48.820 --> 21:49.540
Lawyer Xu,

21:50.419 --> 21:51.820
do you know why

21:51.820 --> 21:53.260
I'm so careful about

21:53.699 --> 21:55.820
and especially careful about safety?

21:57.139 --> 21:57.820
Why?

21:59.939 --> 22:01.300
Because my father taught me.

22:26.020 --> 22:26.780
Lawyer Xu

22:27.540 --> 22:28.980
Do you know why

22:28.980 --> 22:30.580
I especially obey the traffic rules

22:30.859 --> 22:33.060
and am especially careful about safety?

22:34.260 --> 22:34.859
Why?

22:35.100 --> 22:36.540
Because my father taught me.

22:46.139 --> 22:49.139
It seems that the quarrel is quite big.

22:49.820 --> 22:50.580
I think

22:50.820 --> 22:52.060
maybe we shouldn't

22:52.740 --> 22:54.659
let Xu stay for dinner?

22:56.100 --> 22:57.100
Let's see how it goes.

22:59.020 --> 23:00.580
We already made plans.

23:13.500 --> 23:14.300
Let me walk you up.

23:14.580 --> 23:15.459
No need, Lawyer Xu.

23:15.899 --> 23:17.020
The case is over,

23:17.139 --> 23:17.659
and I won't

23:17.659 --> 23:18.580
bother you like this again.

23:18.980 --> 23:19.820
I have guests at home.

23:20.219 --> 23:20.939
I'll go up now.

23:23.020 --> 23:24.740
Goodbye, Lawyer Xu.

23:44.459 --> 23:45.899
Here, have some water.

23:46.540 --> 23:47.260
Mingying,

23:48.820 --> 23:49.820
I feel like

23:51.020 --> 23:53.100
the tears in my eyes

23:54.379 --> 23:55.020
are the water

23:55.020 --> 23:57.020
that got into my head

23:57.899 --> 23:59.139
when I used to peek at him from the classroom railing.

24:02.500 --> 24:04.619
Come on, wipe the water.

24:06.899 --> 24:07.980
So embarrassing.

24:08.980 --> 24:10.219
So humiliating.

24:10.780 --> 24:11.580
Now,

24:13.020 --> 24:14.179
whenever I recall

24:14.179 --> 24:15.419
those days,

24:16.619 --> 24:17.219
I just...

24:26.300 --> 24:26.859
We just

24:26.859 --> 24:27.899
spent a wonderful time together

24:27.899 --> 24:29.340
a few days ago.

24:30.219 --> 24:31.699
I thought Xu Huaisong

24:32.340 --> 24:33.219
would hold your hand

24:33.219 --> 24:34.820
and watch fireworks

24:35.419 --> 24:37.419
this New Year's Eve.

24:39.260 --> 24:40.100
Fireworks?

24:42.060 --> 24:43.899
When we watched fireworks ten years ago,

24:44.540 --> 24:46.300
he wanted to hold someone else's hand.

24:47.500 --> 24:48.500
I even imagined

24:48.500 --> 24:49.780
a mutual crush story.

24:50.179 --> 24:51.060
I even fantasized

24:51.899 --> 24:53.580
about doing this and that with him.

24:55.659 --> 24:57.060
But from the beginning,

24:57.980 --> 24:59.659
he knew I was writing about him.

25:00.139 --> 25:01.020
He even discussed with me

25:01.020 --> 25:02.020
this imagined story,

25:02.859 --> 25:05.020
from the plot to the character design,

25:05.219 --> 25:06.540
to the female lead's inner thoughts.

25:07.859 --> 25:09.100
Whenever I think about it now,

25:09.100 --> 25:10.619
I just want to disappear on the spot.

25:11.300 --> 25:12.619
What I wanted to see were the fireworks,

25:12.820 --> 25:14.619
but he was laughing at me.

25:14.699 --> 25:16.300
He looks gentle and refined,

25:16.619 --> 25:18.260
but why is he so indecent?

25:19.100 --> 25:19.820
He has been secretly

25:19.820 --> 25:20.980
laughing at me for so long.

25:24.580 --> 25:25.820
It's not you who should disappear,

25:26.179 --> 25:26.820
but him.

25:28.139 --> 25:28.899
You're right.

25:30.419 --> 25:32.139
Since I can't disappear,

25:33.500 --> 25:34.980
I'll make him disappear.

25:52.500 --> 25:53.139
Deleted.

25:58.260 --> 25:59.139
You've thought it through?

26:17.100 --> 26:18.419
As long as he doesn't exist

26:18.419 --> 26:19.100
in your world,

26:20.699 --> 26:22.260
your embarrassment won't exist either.

26:24.300 --> 26:25.300
It's nothing serious.

26:36.139 --> 26:37.740
I'll borrow your place to sleep for a bit.

26:39.659 --> 26:40.500
You didn't sleep well?

26:42.859 --> 26:44.500
I drank too much strong tea yesterday.

26:47.619 --> 26:48.580
You should rest.

26:49.580 --> 26:50.540
You go to sleep.

27:04.740 --> 27:05.500
Lawyer Xu,

27:06.139 --> 27:06.699
we don't seem

27:06.699 --> 27:07.659
that close yet, do we?

27:09.699 --> 27:10.500
Do you know

27:10.740 --> 27:12.219
why they like Lawyer Liu?

27:13.540 --> 27:15.379
Because he's a lawyer?

27:17.939 --> 27:20.020
Because he's honest,

27:20.419 --> 27:22.179
kind,

27:23.340 --> 27:24.379
and doesn't bully people.

27:24.939 --> 27:27.179
Actions speak louder than words.

27:28.340 --> 27:29.419
The case is over,

27:29.580 --> 27:30.060
and I won't

27:30.060 --> 27:30.980
bother you anymore.

27:31.300 --> 27:33.100
Goodbye, Lawyer Xu.

27:43.139 --> 27:43.820
Pipi,

27:44.980 --> 27:46.459
What should we do now?

28:11.820 --> 28:12.540
Ruan Yu,

28:34.899 --> 28:35.659
are you okay?

28:38.300 --> 28:39.219
Mingying,

28:44.899 --> 28:45.619
what's wrong?

28:46.859 --> 28:48.139
I can delete the friend,

28:49.100 --> 28:50.740
but what about my novel?

28:52.820 --> 28:54.300
My inspiration is gone.

28:55.500 --> 28:56.340
I can't

28:56.340 --> 28:57.740
write anymore.

28:58.659 --> 28:59.580
I understand.

29:00.179 --> 29:01.540
The male lead has fallen,

29:01.540 --> 29:02.699
how can you continue writing?

29:07.619 --> 29:08.540
Maybe

29:10.260 --> 29:11.740
just keep delaying the update.

29:14.659 --> 29:16.379
But the readers are all waiting.

29:19.699 --> 29:22.219
And the deadline in the contract

29:22.219 --> 29:23.139
with your publisher

29:23.419 --> 29:24.580
is

29:25.100 --> 29:26.379
getting closer and closer.

29:27.820 --> 29:29.139
Don't worry about me.

29:29.300 --> 29:30.379
I can handle the chief editor.

29:31.859 --> 29:33.540
As for the readers,

29:35.580 --> 29:36.780
if you force yourself to write now,

29:37.020 --> 29:38.419
but it'll be a mess.

29:38.580 --> 29:39.580
Isn't that

29:39.580 --> 29:40.580
even more irresponsible?

29:44.379 --> 29:44.939
Just

29:46.500 --> 29:47.820
explain it well,

29:48.179 --> 29:49.060
apologize to everyone,

29:50.260 --> 29:51.459
and they'll understand.

30:17.619 --> 30:18.980
[I've made an appointment with Mr. Zhang]

30:19.060 --> 30:21.219
[for 10 AM on Monday,]

30:21.340 --> 30:22.540
[at this café.]

30:22.659 --> 30:24.300
[I'll update you on your ex's progress]

30:24.300 --> 30:25.340
[after the meeting.]

30:26.020 --> 30:28.340
Your friend's ex-boyfriend's progress.

30:39.540 --> 30:40.139
Alright.

30:42.020 --> 30:43.060
Look.

30:45.500 --> 30:47.379
I'd like to apologize to everyone.

30:47.780 --> 30:49.300
I Really Want to Whisper in Your Ear

30:49.699 --> 30:51.580
may have to be suspended.

30:52.020 --> 30:53.939
I may need some time

30:53.939 --> 30:54.740
to get back into the groove.

30:55.500 --> 30:56.379
If I can't

30:56.459 --> 30:57.740
continue this story,

30:58.500 --> 30:59.540
I will refund the subscription coins

30:59.859 --> 31:01.260
to everyone's account.

31:02.379 --> 31:04.060
Thank you for your

31:04.060 --> 31:04.740
support.

31:05.580 --> 31:06.540
We will

31:07.300 --> 31:08.300
meet again.

31:10.179 --> 31:11.340
No, Da.

31:11.699 --> 31:12.540
Our hero

31:12.540 --> 31:13.980
hasn't found his love.

31:14.340 --> 31:15.859
How can you just give up on him?

31:16.379 --> 31:17.379
It's okay, Da.

31:17.540 --> 31:18.260
Too much

31:18.260 --> 31:19.619
has happened recently.

31:19.980 --> 31:20.740
If this story

31:20.740 --> 31:21.580
made you sad,

31:21.780 --> 31:23.060
let's start a new one.

31:49.540 --> 31:50.379
Why are you sitting there

31:50.379 --> 31:51.300
in the middle of the night?

31:51.820 --> 31:52.500
Mingying

31:53.899 --> 31:55.340
Every time I close my eyes,

31:55.980 --> 31:57.659
I see Xu Huaisong.

31:58.699 --> 31:59.379
One of them

31:59.859 --> 32:02.020
is like Hanazawa Rui.

32:03.139 --> 32:03.939
The other one

32:04.580 --> 32:06.780
is like Daoming Si.

32:07.540 --> 32:08.939
You can't sleep

32:08.939 --> 32:09.980
you are losing sleep.

32:10.379 --> 32:11.300
Think about him,

32:11.820 --> 32:13.619
he might be sleeping soundly right now.

32:14.459 --> 32:15.260
Is it worth it?

32:16.980 --> 32:17.780
No, it's not.

32:19.379 --> 32:21.300
But I can't control myself.

32:24.939 --> 32:26.179
You are almost

32:26.179 --> 32:27.419
in a state of heartbreak.

32:30.260 --> 32:31.419
That's how it is at night.

32:32.580 --> 32:34.020
But even if you can't sleep,

32:34.540 --> 32:36.020
lying down is also a kind of rest.

32:39.419 --> 32:40.139
Come on up.

32:42.379 --> 32:43.060
Hurry up!

32:53.379 --> 32:54.179
Stop thinking.

32:54.580 --> 32:56.540
He should be the one worrying.

33:39.219 --> 33:39.859
Ruan Yu.

33:40.340 --> 33:41.500
I'm here to apologize.

33:52.699 --> 33:53.459
I'm sorry.

33:53.820 --> 33:55.179
I should've told you earlier.

33:55.179 --> 33:56.260
I shouldn't have kept it from you.

33:57.219 --> 33:58.980
Leave now, or I'll call the police.

34:00.820 --> 34:01.260
It's him!

34:01.260 --> 34:02.179
-Forgive me. -Hurry up!

34:02.859 --> 34:03.699
Stop asking!

34:03.699 --> 34:04.820
Hurry up, drag him away!

34:04.820 --> 34:05.659
Let me finish!

34:09.740 --> 34:10.939
Ms. Ruan, I'm sorry.

34:11.899 --> 34:14.020
I just want you to help me with...

34:14.459 --> 34:15.459
Bullying my daughter,

34:15.459 --> 34:16.699
and now you want me to help you?

34:17.619 --> 34:18.540
No way!

34:18.739 --> 34:19.219
Not even

34:21.139 --> 34:22.020
a window!

34:37.299 --> 34:37.940
[I'm sorry.]

34:38.580 --> 34:40.139
[I should've told you sooner.]

34:41.060 --> 34:42.619
[I want to explain to you in person.]

34:43.739 --> 34:46.299
[Do you have time these days?]

35:16.100 --> 35:18.259
[Ruan Yu, I saw your Weibo post.]

35:18.739 --> 35:20.339
[You haven't updated your novel.]

35:20.659 --> 35:21.619
[Is there a reason?]

35:21.900 --> 35:22.940
[I mean,]

35:23.179 --> 35:23.580
[if it's]

35:23.580 --> 35:24.699
[a legal issue,]

35:24.860 --> 35:26.259
[we can provide after-sales service.]

35:26.900 --> 35:27.699
[Or]

35:28.420 --> 35:29.779
[is there another reason?]

35:30.500 --> 35:31.100
It seems that Ruan Yu

35:31.100 --> 35:32.420
isn't planning to respond to me either.

35:34.500 --> 35:35.299
I can see it.

35:41.299 --> 35:42.540
Send another one.

35:44.500 --> 35:46.060
If you consider me as your friend...

35:51.299 --> 35:52.699
What do you mean by "if"?

35:52.940 --> 35:54.380
I am his friend.

35:54.380 --> 35:55.420
There's no "if" about it.

35:55.420 --> 35:56.619
Just do it.

36:05.299 --> 36:05.900
Wait.

36:08.219 --> 36:08.900
Are you done?

36:09.219 --> 36:09.900
Our schedule

36:09.900 --> 36:10.900
is packed for today.

36:10.900 --> 36:12.219
We can't afford any delays.

36:12.739 --> 36:13.299
Finally.

36:14.020 --> 36:14.980
Who's been

36:15.219 --> 36:16.420
texting me nonstop?

36:25.420 --> 36:26.179
Ruan Yu's reply.

36:28.659 --> 36:29.779
Thanks for asking, Mr. Liu.

36:30.619 --> 36:31.739
The hiatus is because the male lead

36:31.739 --> 36:32.860
has broken character for me.

36:33.540 --> 36:35.299
I'm no longer invested in this story.

36:36.420 --> 36:37.580
What does "breaking character" mean?

36:39.580 --> 36:40.100
In this context,

36:40.100 --> 36:41.020
it means

36:41.020 --> 36:43.100
the character's persona

36:43.779 --> 36:44.580
The character collapses.

36:44.779 --> 36:46.420
I'm not interested in

36:47.299 --> 36:48.219
the male protagonist in the story.

36:54.540 --> 36:55.259
Bro,

36:55.540 --> 36:56.540
I can only help you up to here.

36:57.020 --> 36:58.900
You go the rest of the way yourself.

37:02.900 --> 37:04.460
By the way, this afternoon,

37:04.460 --> 37:05.699
people from SG

37:05.699 --> 37:07.060
will come to discuss the new annual cooperation.

37:07.380 --> 37:08.139
Don't forget.

37:14.619 --> 37:16.739
Jackson, welcome to Zhikun.

37:16.819 --> 37:17.819
Nice to meet you.

37:18.339 --> 37:19.100
Nice to meet you.

38:08.460 --> 38:09.179
Don't worry.

38:09.739 --> 38:10.779
I'm almost home.

38:13.219 --> 38:13.819
How was it?

38:14.060 --> 38:14.819
After a day of fun,

38:14.819 --> 38:16.219
do you feel completely relaxed

38:16.219 --> 38:17.339
and all your worries are gone?

38:18.779 --> 38:19.619
The flashy world

38:19.619 --> 38:21.100
is indeed the best elixir.

38:22.100 --> 38:22.860
Tonight,

38:23.299 --> 38:24.380
I'm sure I'll have a good sleep.

38:24.860 --> 38:25.699
Of course.

38:25.980 --> 38:27.420
I can sleep well too.

38:28.139 --> 38:29.219
I'm going to take a shower.

38:30.060 --> 38:30.739
You should rest early.

38:30.739 --> 38:31.619
We have work tomorrow.

38:32.139 --> 38:32.900
I'm home.

38:33.100 --> 38:34.299
Love you. Bye.

38:56.619 --> 38:58.420
Lawyer Xu, wear this.

38:59.619 --> 39:00.380
It's new.

39:00.580 --> 39:02.020
I bought it at the supermarket

39:02.219 --> 39:03.779
after you visited my house last time.

39:04.500 --> 39:05.100
Thank you.

40:11.860 --> 40:12.900
How do you know

40:13.299 --> 40:14.420
I'm from Suzhou?

40:19.940 --> 40:22.139
[Ruan Yu, you're done.]

40:37.299 --> 40:38.580
[The effects of the pills]

40:39.259 --> 40:40.860
[seem to be wearing off too quickly.]

40:46.259 --> 40:48.860
[I think just him disappearing isn't enough.]

40:50.259 --> 40:53.460
[I might need to disappear as well.]

41:12.580 --> 41:13.259
Ruan Yu.

41:16.739 --> 41:17.420
Ruan Yu.

41:20.540 --> 41:21.420
Young man,

41:21.540 --> 41:22.380
stop knocking.

41:22.420 --> 41:23.259
There's no one home.

41:24.219 --> 41:25.540
Do you know where she went?

41:26.339 --> 41:27.420
How would I know?

41:27.699 --> 41:28.139
But this morning,

41:28.139 --> 41:29.060
I saw her

41:29.060 --> 41:30.020
leaving with

41:30.179 --> 41:31.500
a big suitcase

41:31.500 --> 41:32.219
during my workout.

41:32.420 --> 41:33.900
She must be going on a long trip.

42:00.739 --> 42:01.460
Why are you here?

42:02.460 --> 42:03.219
Why can't I come?

42:05.500 --> 42:07.500
What's up? You look down.

42:14.259 --> 42:15.940
The rumors have died down,

42:16.860 --> 42:18.779
and it's time to resume the novel updates.

42:19.659 --> 42:21.940
But I just can't write anymore.

42:22.299 --> 42:24.020
It's normal to get stuck when writing a novel.

42:24.219 --> 42:25.299
You used to get stuck too.

42:25.779 --> 42:26.619
Just relax.

42:29.100 --> 42:30.299
This time is different.

42:31.299 --> 42:33.179
The prototype of the male lead is right beside me.

42:33.739 --> 42:34.380
How can I possibly

42:34.380 --> 42:36.020
continue writing as if nothing happened?

42:37.060 --> 42:38.299
Aren't you two just talking about work

42:38.299 --> 42:39.139
and having a video call?

42:39.420 --> 42:39.940
What's going on?

42:41.779 --> 42:42.659
Did you turn Chapter 23

42:42.659 --> 42:43.739
into reality?

42:44.940 --> 42:45.900
How's that possible?

42:47.179 --> 42:48.259
What can't be written?

42:48.259 --> 42:49.219
Come on, let me see.

42:50.420 --> 42:51.219
I'll find it for you.

42:51.219 --> 42:51.860
I'll find it.

42:53.020 --> 42:54.219
You, just sit.

42:55.779 --> 42:57.380
Let me check the draft.

42:58.779 --> 42:59.299
Here.

43:00.980 --> 43:01.659
Here it is.

43:10.060 --> 43:11.219
Ms. Ruan,

43:12.259 --> 43:13.940
if I'm not mistaken,

43:13.940 --> 43:15.020
you've only updated

43:15.020 --> 43:16.219
like

43:16.219 --> 43:17.219
five

43:17.699 --> 43:18.659
words.

43:19.100 --> 43:20.219
Do you even need to look for it?

43:22.540 --> 43:24.339
The moment I open the document,

43:24.860 --> 43:25.500
I don't think of Xu Huaisong

43:25.500 --> 43:27.259
from high school,

43:27.980 --> 43:29.500
but Lawyer Xu's face.

43:30.980 --> 43:32.100
I can even hear

43:32.100 --> 43:33.699
his sharp comments.

43:35.420 --> 43:38.259
[On the day He Shiqian was on duty,]

43:38.860 --> 43:40.819
[he deliberately sweeps slowly,]

43:41.420 --> 43:44.659
[because Lin Xisheng is nearby.]

43:45.460 --> 43:47.299
[Lawyers' time is very precious.]

43:49.819 --> 43:51.420
[Lin Xisheng]

43:51.860 --> 43:55.139
[also has photos of He Shiqian]

43:55.739 --> 43:57.259
[taken at the sports meet]

43:57.699 --> 44:01.659
[in the class teacher's camera.]

44:06.860 --> 44:07.380
[Miss Ruan,]

44:07.380 --> 44:08.500
[I need to remind you that]

44:08.819 --> 44:10.060
[taking photos of others]

44:10.219 --> 44:12.020
[without their permission]

44:12.619 --> 44:14.179
[carries certain legal risks.]

44:19.779 --> 44:21.060
It's not that I don't want to write.

44:21.900 --> 44:23.380
I just can't

44:23.380 --> 44:24.699
put a word on it.

44:27.259 --> 44:28.460
Based on my experience,

44:29.299 --> 44:30.299
there are two solutions

44:30.900 --> 44:32.779
to this problem.

44:33.339 --> 44:35.179
Either stay away from him,

44:35.699 --> 44:36.339
or get close to him.

44:37.100 --> 44:38.619
You can try to get close to him.

44:38.860 --> 44:39.900
Maybe you'll get new inspirations.

44:40.179 --> 44:41.460
Get close to him?

44:42.299 --> 44:42.739
But...

44:43.139 --> 44:43.500
what if

44:43.500 --> 44:44.659
I lose interest in him?

44:45.420 --> 44:46.819
That's less likely

44:46.819 --> 44:47.659
than you

44:47.659 --> 44:48.619
getting back together.

44:50.219 --> 44:51.219
I'm tired.

44:52.139 --> 44:53.259
I'm gonna take a nap.

44:53.900 --> 44:54.619
You're good.
